# aur.list — AUR packages, installed via the helper (paru) bootstrapped in
# phase 10. One per line; # comments and blanks ignored. Keep this short: every
# entry is a from-source build, so only put here what the official repos lack.
#
# No theme-settings GUI here (e.g. nwg-look): theme/icon/cursor/accent are owned
# end-to-end by the Quickshell Settings app (scripts/colorscheme.sh writes the
# GTK/Qt/KDE config). One place to manage everything — no extra app.
gpu-screen-recorder        # GPU-encoded screen capture + replay buffer (VAAPI/NVENC)
fresh-editor               # Fresh — terminal IDE (default editor); single static binary, built-in LSP
